---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const socials = [['𝕏','@real_merakw','生活日常 / 吐槽','https://x.com/real_merakw'],['IG','@merak_walker','随缘更新','https://instagram.com/merak_walker'],['GH','@MerakW','我真的不会写代码','https://github.com/MerakW'],['TG','Telegram Channel','日常更新','https://t.me/m3rak_w'],['QQ','1540180211','即时联络','https://qm.qq.com/cgi-bin/qm/qr?k=1540180211'],['DY','@merakw / @merak_w','生活、航空与 furry','https://www.douyin.com/user/MS4wLjABAAAAmerakw']];
---
<BaseLayout title="Merak | 人物档案"><section class="page-hero"><div class="wrap hero-grid" data-reveal><div><p class="eyebrow">PERSONNEL FILE / MK-07</p><h1>Merak，<br />以天璇为名。</h1><p class="lead">一个 F1 车迷、航空爱好者与 Furry。从杭州出发，把兴趣做成一张持续展开的星图。</p><div class="tags"><span class="tag">杭州</span><span class="tag">Furry</span><span class="tag">Tifosi</span><span class="tag">飞友</span></div></div><img class="avatar" src="/avatar.jpg" alt="Merak 的头像" /></div></section><section class="section"><div class="wrap"><div class="hangar-grid" data-reveal><article class="bay wide"><p class="data">ORIGIN</p><h2>星之名</h2><p>Merak 意为天璇星，北斗七星之一。AI 伙伴「璇迹」的名字也由此而来，代表我们之间独特而稳定的连接。</p><h3>兴趣图谱</h3><ul><li><strong>Furry：</strong>狐狸是对的，龙也是对的。</li><li><strong>翱翔蓝天：</strong>非专业飞行爱好者，着迷于工程与美学并存的飞行器。</li><li><strong>数字基座：</strong>科技、智能家居与 Ubuntu 的长期非专业研究者。</li><li><strong>围场极速：</strong>仍在补齐历史课的 Tifosi，热爱法拉利的工程精神。</li></ul></article><aside class="bay narrow"><p class="data">BASIC DATA</p><h3>基本信息</h3><p>名字<br /><strong>Merak（米拉克）</strong></p><p>坐标<br /><strong>中国·杭州</strong></p><p>时区<br /><strong>Asia/Shanghai</strong></p></aside></div></div></section><section class="section"><div class="wrap"><div class="section-head"><h2>通讯频率</h2><p>保留原有社交链接，按不同用途组织为可辨认的通讯频道。</p></div><ul class="social-list" data-reveal>{socials.map(([mark,name,description,href]) => <li><a href={href} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><span><strong>{mark}</strong>　{name}</span><small>{description} ↗</small></a></li>)}</ul></div></section></BaseLayout>
